- Status: Stopped at iteration 24/200 due to KL > 0.25 threshold
- Reason: KL divergence reached 0.3806, exceeding --max-kl 0.25
- This explains fast training time (8.7 min vs expected 90 min)

IMPLICATION FOR V6:
⚠️ LR 3e-5 was too aggressive for fine-tuning from v4_best.pt
   The resumed model immediately diverged on new data
   
RECOMMENDATION FOR V6:
Option A (PREFERRED): Lower LR to 1e-5 or 5e-6
  - Keep --max-kl 0.25
  - Expected: Slower divergence, more stable learning
  - Command: --lr 1e-5 --lr-warmup-iters 20
  
Option B (RISKY): Increase KL tolerance to 0.5
  - Keep LR at 3e-5
  - Risk: Policy collapse or instability
  - Not recommended

